About Us

Tərəqqi Liseyi is an online learning and testing platform designed to help students and teachers in their educational journey. We provide a wide range of educational materials and interactive tests to enhance your learning experience.

Interactive Tests

Take interactive tests in various subjects and difficulty levels to assess your knowledge and improve your skills.

Personalized Learning

Tailor your learning experience with personalized study materials and recommendations based on your progress and preferences.

Teacher Resources

Teachers can create and share tests, track student progress, and access valuable resources to support their teaching.
